name: Ground Fighter "Roll" Shirt - Heather Grey
description:
Collaboration design inspired by the great work of our friends over at kristensphoto.com. This shirt combines Ground Fighter's "Roll" design with the dynamic grappling action of jiu-jitsu captured by Kristen.

Our shirts are not only lightweight, super soft, and comfortable for casual wear, but also extra durable for active wear.

- 4.3 oz, made with 60% Cotton/40% Polyester
- Machine washable and preshrunk to minimize shrinkage
- Ground Fighter custom label
- Regular fit (see size chart)
- Printed in the USA

Note: T-shirts are pre-shrunk, but may still shrink in the wash. We recommend washing them in cold water and hanging to dry in order to avoid shrinkage.

Photo by Kristen Mendes
www.kristensphoto.com

Design by Isaac Vazquez 
www.behance.net/isaacvazquez

*All images and designs copyright © of Ground Fighter 2013

name: Ground Fighter "Ready Set Roll" Ranked Rash Guards
description:
Short sleeve black body ranked rash guards approved by IBJJF and all other No Gi competitions. Rash guards are fully sublimated so the design is part of the fabric.

- BJJ competition approved
- Dye sublimated designs never fade, peel or crack
- Longer cut torso to prevent ride up
- Naturally anti-bacterial and anti-odor
- Moisture wicking, breathable and comfortable
- 8 panels for a better body fit
- Reinforced flatlock stitching lays flat for less irritation & more durability
- Made from premium lycra material (88% Poly, 12% Spandex)
- 3/4" collar lays flat against your neck to prevent chaffing

*Because this product is made of lycra material, it is not eligible for return or exchange due to hygiene concerns. Be sure to check the size chart before ordering.

Design by Isaac Vazquez
www.behance.net/isaacvazquez

*All images and designs copyright © of Ground Fighter 2013
